subscribe.sSYSTEM:
`a!subscriber-role` Sets the subscriber role.
`a!subscriber-authorized @Authorized` Sets the role to grant the subscriber. 
`a!subscriber-log` Keeps the log of those who are given the subscriber role.
`a!subscriber-set channel & a!subscriber-channel close` Youtube subscriber counter sets.**COMING SOON!**

helpMenu.hDescription:
If you don't know how to use the command, you can report the bug by [Our Support Server](https://discord.gg/NAzGC2cxXR)

**user menu** `a!help-user` Opens the User menu.
**entertainment menu** `a!help-entertainment` A useful menu for those who are bored.
**moderation menu** `a!help-moderation` has been adjusted for the convenience of privileges.
**producer menu** `a!help-producer | a!help-owner` Opens commands available to the producer.
**update menu** `a!updates | a!uptades` Shows the bot's updates.
**update versions** `a!update-v | a!update-version` Displays incoming update versions.
**bot menu** `a!help-bot` Shows things like bot's invite link.
